Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:11.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,索恩 我想跟你私下谈谈\N{\rYUANWEN}I need to speak with you privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我们去兜兜风吧  -好的长官\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's take a ride. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.60,0:00:15.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他把一切都告诉我了 给了我完整简报\N{\rYUANWEN}He told me everything, gave me the full briefing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:16.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,梯队简报\N{\rYUANWEN}The Echelon Briefing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:20.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,公民共和军会把世界带回来\N{\rYUANWEN}Jadis: The CRM will bring the world back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,告诉我你不会去追杀他们\N{\rYUANWEN}Tell me you won't come after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:25.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不 因为我们要去找他们\N{\rYUANWEN}No. Because we are coming for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会拿到档案\N{\rYUANWEN}We're gonna get the dossier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.57,0:00:29.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他会得到梯队简报\N{\rYUANWEN}He's gonna get the Echelon Briefing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找出他们所做的\N{\rYUANWEN}and find out everything that they do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:34.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而这个城市却不知道的一切\N{\rYUANWEN}that the city doesn't know about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:37.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会帮助城市阻止他们\N{\rYUANWEN}We're gonna help the city stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我都记得\N{\rYUANWEN}Rick: I remember it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:45.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是什么样子\N{\rYUANWEN}What it was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:50.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们曾经是谁 现在是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Who we were. Who we are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我叫米琼恩\N{\rYUANWEN}Michonne: My name is Michonne.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.56,0:00:59.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我失去了一个人\N{\rYUANWEN}I lost someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:02.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很多年前就失去了\N{\rYUANWEN}Years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.23,0:01:05.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们二人都具有成为公民共和军所需的特质\N{\rYUANWEN}Okafor: Both of them have something I believe the CRM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:10.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有着发展成为其所需形态的潜力\N{\rYUANWEN}needs to become what it needs to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:12.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,人是一种资源\N{\rYUANWEN}Jadis: People are a resource.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:16.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道如何建造\N{\rYUANWEN}Nat: I know how to build things,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:18.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如何摧毁\N{\rYUANWEN}and I know how to burn things,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:21.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但末世之中需要的不仅仅是这些\N{\rYUANWEN}but it takes more than that at the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.96,0:01:28.55,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你试图逃跑过四次\N{\rYUANWEN}Beale: You tried to escape four times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:29.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你为什么会在这里\N{\rYUANWEN}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.43,0:01:36.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,外面有你爱的人\N{\rYUANWEN}Thorne: There's someone you love out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:42.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你还爱我吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Michonne: Do you still love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一直都爱\N{\rYUANWEN}Rick: Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听起来很简单对不对\N{\rYUANWEN}Michonne: It sounds simple, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:56.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们分头进去 你去拿简报\N{\rYUANWEN}We each go in. You get the briefing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我去拿她留下的档案\N{\rYUANWEN}I get the dossier she left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:02.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们让城市知晓我们已知的一切 然后回家\N{\rYUANWEN}We bring what we know to the city, then go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:05.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一起回家\N{\rYUANWEN}Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从来都不会那么简单\N{\rYUANWEN}It's never that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:19.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我是瑞克·格莱姆斯军士长\N{\rYUANWEN}Rick: I'm Sergeant Major Rick Grimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:21.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可能以为我死了\N{\rYUANWEN}You probably think I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他说我不必害怕\N{\rYUANWEN}He said I didn't need to be scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那不过是“摧毁”\N{\rYUANWEN}that it was just"the burning. "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你真的在这里\N{\rYUANWEN}You're really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:34.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你向他们汇报了情况 现在告诉我是怎么回事\N{\rYUANWEN}You gave them the debrief. Now tell me what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,当时出现气流\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, there was turbulence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:40.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们降低了飞行高度想冲出来\N{\rYUANWEN}We - We went low to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:42.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-被闪电击中  -嗯\N{\rYUANWEN}We were struck by lightning. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:46.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,掉到水上滑行 贝休恩把我推出来\N{\rYUANWEN}We were going down over water, and Bethune shoved me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:47.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她救了我的命\N{\rYUANWEN}She saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.86,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,却没能活下来 只救下了我\N{\rYUANWEN}Not hers, mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你吸收她进来\N{\rYUANWEN}So thank you for bringing her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:53.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不是 是你招募她的\N{\rYUANWEN}No, you brought her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们何不直接说是奥卡福呢\N{\rYUANWEN}Why don't we just say it was Okafor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们只是在继续发扬他的事业\N{\rYUANWEN}That we were just keeping his thing going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.58,0:04:05.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我以前觉得放弃\N{\rYUANWEN}I used to think that giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是缺乏个性\N{\rYUANWEN}meant a lack of character
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.46,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,意志薄弱\N{\rYUANWEN}and a- - a weak will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你和我 我们放弃了那么多才走到这步\N{\rYUANWEN}But you and I, we gave up so much to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:20.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,现在我意识到放弃可以是力量的象征\N{\rYUANWEN}And now I realize that giving up can be a sign of strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:24.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,对比自己更重要的事情的承诺\N{\rYUANWEN}A commitment to something bigger than oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:28.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放弃让我明白了我们在这里真正的目的\N{\rYUANWEN}Giving up made me understand what we're really doing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,希望你也能明白\N{\rYUANWEN}Hopefully, you will understand, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.11,0:04:34.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望可以\N{\rYUANWEN}Iwant to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很高兴你活下来了 瑞克\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm glad you made it, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:41.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家很需要你\N{\rYUANWEN}You are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:42.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这取决于我们 而不是\N{\rYUANWEN}It is up to us, but not like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:45.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,像奥卡福说的那样\N{\rYUANWEN}Okafor said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,奥卡福 他\N{\rYUANWEN}Okafor, he
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:52.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,身在曹营心在汉 没有全身心投入进来\N{\rYUANWEN}He was never really here, not in the way he should have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:53.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以他才死了\N{\rYUANWEN}That's why he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:57.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你活下来了 我活下来了\N{\rYUANWEN}But you lived. I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们注定要成为其中一员\N{\rYUANWEN}We are meant to be a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是时候忘掉他的废话了\N{\rYUANWEN}It's time to let go of his bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:06.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,给我指明另一条路\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, show me the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,威胁解除\N{\rYUANWEN}Threat neutralized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我去周围搜查一下\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm gonna take a sweep of the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他想跟你谈谈\N{\rYUANWEN}He wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:31.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,瑞克\N{\rYUANWEN}Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就是这里\N{\rYUANWEN}This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:50.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从没必要做这事\N{\rYUANWEN}I never had to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:53.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从没必要为成为公民而杀掉六个行尸 因为我\N{\rYUANWEN}I never had to do my six for citizenship because I- -
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.92,0:06:56.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从来没成为过一个真正的公民\N{\rYUANWEN}I never really became a citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:02.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,世界终结和开始\N{\rYUANWEN}The end of the world and the beginning of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.72,0:07:05.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,死的会是我们 瑞克\N{\rYUANWEN}And we're the dead ones, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们跟他们有点类似\N{\rYUANWEN}We're kind of like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:12.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但他们杀戮只是为了谋求食物或出于强迫\N{\rYUANWEN}But they only kill for food or out of compulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:15.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-对不对  -是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Isn't that right? It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:19.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们的科学家还是没有解决方案\N{\rYUANWEN}Our scientists haven't figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:22.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许以后都不会有\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe they never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:27.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但我们 另一种死去的人\N{\rYUANWEN}But us, the other kind of dead ones,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:30.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们有这个\N{\rYUANWEN}we have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:34.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杀戮之剑即是赋予生命之剑\N{\rYUANWEN}The sword that kills is the sword that gives life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就是我们 我们就是这把剑\N{\rYUANWEN}And that's us. We're the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:41.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行动前一天 我让助理和副官们退下了\N{\rYUANWEN}I have my aides and lieutenants leave me in solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,独留我一个人\N{\rYUANWEN}the day before an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢被分心\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't like distractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我独自决定前进的道路\N{\rYUANWEN}I alone decided the path ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,独自感受它的重量\N{\rYUANWEN}and I alone want to feel the weight of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:54.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从无例外\N{\rYUANWEN}I never interrupt that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你来了\N{\rYUANWEN}But you are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,经历这一切之后\N{\rYUANWEN}After everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.69,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,令我自愧不如\N{\rYUANWEN}And I am humbled by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.53,0:08:07.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 我会同你共度些时光\N{\rYUANWEN}So, I'll share some time with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许甚至会让你承担部分重量\N{\rYUANWEN}maybe even ask you to carry some of that weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.16,0:10:15.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,斯托克斯警官 你在里面吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Woman: Officer Stokes? Are you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:50.03,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把枪放桌子上\N{\rYUANWEN}Put your gun on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.16,0:10:59.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那个带刀片的假肢\N{\rYUANWEN}That prosthetic with the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,放我前面 离你远点\N{\rYUANWEN}In front of me. Away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:23.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你能反思下自己的人生\N{\rYUANWEN}I want you to reflect on your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:27.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,此刻之前和之后的所有的人生经历\N{\rYUANWEN}On all your lives before and after.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所有之前和之后的事情\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI the before and afters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:35.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,此刻之前你所做的一切\N{\rYUANWEN}AlI the things you did before this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为\N{\rYUANWEN}Because.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:40.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下一刻之后\N{\rYUANWEN}after this next moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一切都会改变\N{\rYUANWEN}everything will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:49.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,为了让其他人活下来\N{\rYUANWEN}What was the worst thing you did
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你做过的最糟糕的事是什么\N{\rYUANWEN}to make sure someone else survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:07.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我用牙齿杀过人\N{\rYUANWEN}I killed someone with my teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,就像他们一样\N{\rYUANWEN}Like they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,很抱歉你不得不那么做\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm sorry you had to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,倒是不必\N{\rYUANWEN}Oh, you don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:16.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可还是很不爽 对不对\N{\rYUANWEN}Still, it's a damn thing, isn't it?
