Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:47.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们摧毁了它 连同它的校园殖民地\N{\rYUANWEN}We destroyed it, along with its Campus Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:53.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,18小时后 我们将采取最后行动\N{\rYUANWEN}And in 18 hours, we will take our final action
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让我们成为这片大陆上 也许是世界上\N{\rYUANWEN}to leave us as the supreme force on this continent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:20:59.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,最强大的力量\N{\rYUANWEN}maybe the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会摧毁波特兰\N{\rYUANWEN}We will destroy Portland.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:04.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们告诉共和国的人民 公民共和军是做什么的\N{\rYUANWEN}We tell the Civic Republic what the CRM does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比如轰炸 还有他们做的其他事情\N{\rYUANWEN}Like the bombing, whatever else they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我们不说 谁还会说呢\N{\rYUANWEN}If we don't, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有人\N{\rYUANWEN}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,绝不能丢下人们不管\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't leave people behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就是我们要做的事\N{\rYUANWEN}This is the shit we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,作为对波特兰陷落的回应\N{\rYUANWEN}In response to the loss of Portland,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们最后的同盟伙伴\N{\rYUANWEN}our last alliance partner- -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:30.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们将作为又一起悲剧 神秘和令人震惊的\N{\rYUANWEN}which we will report as another tragic, mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:34.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,事件报道 公民共和国军\N{\rYUANWEN}shocking incident- the Civic Republic Military
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:36.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,将宣布对城市实施戒严令\N{\rYUANWEN}will declare martial law on the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:38.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,废除议会\N{\rYUANWEN}doing away with the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.22,0:21:39.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,自由的代价太高了\N{\rYUANWEN}Stakes are too high for freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:42.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,随着公民共和军控制城市和我们同盟伙伴的死亡\N{\rYUANWEN}With the city under CRM control and our Alliance partners dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:45.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们将在全国范围内进军\N{\rYUANWEN}we will march across this country
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,进一步消除任何日益增长的竞争\N{\rYUANWEN}and further eliminate any growing competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:50.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们将夺取他们的资源 确保霸权\N{\rYUANWEN}We will take their resources and ensure supremacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后\N{\rYUANWEN}And maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:56.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也许我们就能存活了\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe we get to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:06.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,气泡窗口会被遮拦\N{\rYUANWEN}Man#3: Bubble windows will be in blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:08.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,孩子们不会看到或者听到\N{\rYUANWEN}The children will not see or hear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:10.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个城市里发生的一切\N{\rYUANWEN}what is happening to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.46,0:22:13.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,至关重要的是 要保持稳定\N{\rYUANWEN}It is critical to remain even, to be steady,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:16.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要被孩子们将要经历的创伤\N{\rYUANWEN}to not give in to the trauma the children will experience- -
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:19.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或者是参与部队将要经历的一切所影响\N{\rYUANWEN}or that the participating forces will experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:25.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会坐简迪斯的直升机回公民共和国\N{\rYUANWEN}We'll get back to the Civic Republic in Jadis's helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.47,0:22:29.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会带大家飞到他们意想不到的跳伞点加油\N{\rYUANWEN}I'll fly us to jump points for the refuels they won't expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:34.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,基地有任何变化 通过对讲机告诉我\N{\rYUANWEN}Anything changes on base, key the walkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:38.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会尽快回到你身边\N{\rYUANWEN}I'lI get back to you when I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.28,0:22:41.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我还在的话\N{\rYUANWEN}If I can be gotten back to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:50.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你在等人呼叫吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You expecting a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:54.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是索恩\N{\rYUANWEN}That was Thorne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.75,0:22:56.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,她经历了这些\N{\rYUANWEN}She went through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:59.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想如果能跟她谈谈应该挺好\N{\rYUANWEN}Thought it would be good to talk it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.59,0:23:03.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,士兵们应该让孩子们把注意力放在\N{\rYUANWEN}Man#3: Soldiers should put the children's focus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们为他们提供的舒适物品上\N{\rYUANWEN}on the comfort items we'll furnish them with.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:09.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不要说“一切都会好起来的”\N{\rYUANWEN}Avoid saying, "It's going to be okay. "
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:12.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只说“他们”会没事的\N{\rYUANWEN}Just say"they" will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:15.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们中的任何一个都可能成为\N{\rYUANWEN}Any one of them could prove to be the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:18.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们文明幸存的差异因素\N{\rYUANWEN}in our civilization's survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:20.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们将在很多方面 进行清理\N{\rYUANWEN}We will, in many ways, scavenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:28.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在发生了这一切之后\N{\rYUANWEN}After everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.24,0:23:32.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在所有的逃跑尝试之后 就在此时此地\N{\rYUANWEN}after all the escape attempts to right here, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:38.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我认为下一个十年的领导者\N{\rYUANWEN}I think that the next leader in the next decade,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可能就是你\N{\rYUANWEN}that might be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:44.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这么多年 多次试图逃离之后\N{\rYUANWEN}After trying to get away so many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.18,0:23:48.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你发现自己自由了 对我们来说你已经死了\N{\rYUANWEN}after so many years you found yourself free, dead to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.85,0:23:52.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你可以去任何你想去的地方\N{\rYUANWEN}You could've gone wherever it was you wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:53.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可你却回来了\N{\rYUANWEN}And you came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:23:58.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你会成为一个有影响力的故事\N{\rYUANWEN}You've become a powerful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.23,0:24:00.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一个强有力的象征 一个公民共和军\N{\rYUANWEN}A powerful symbol, one the CRM
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.36,0:24:02.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,用来讲述以赢得人心的故事\N{\rYUANWEN}may need to tell to win the hearts of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:06.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,因为他们将看到自己的某些自由再次被推迟\N{\rYUANWEN}who will see some of their freedoms delayed yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.86,0:24:11.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我牺牲过 奥卡福也牺牲过\N{\rYUANWEN}I sacrificed. Okafor sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:13.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我希望你也能这样\N{\rYUANWEN}I would expect the same for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.25,0:24:15.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你说自己已经有过牺牲\N{\rYUANWEN}But you said it- - you already have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.34,0:24:22.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,听说你最亲近的人在这之中死去了 是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Who's the person closest to you who's died in all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.59,0:24:30.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.81,0:24:36.43,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我切断了那个人的喉咙去救他\N{\rYUANWEN}He's who I saved tearing out that man's throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.35,0:24:40.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你最后都没能救到他吗\N{\rYUANWEN}But you couldn't save him in the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.86,0:24:46.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\rYUANWEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.86,0:24:50.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你\N{\rYUANWEN}What if I told you you would never have to suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.41,0:24:52.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你再也不用承受那种损失了\N{\rYUANWEN}that kind of loss again,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.41,0:24:53.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不管你要去哪里\N{\rYUANWEN}that wherever you were running to,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.00,0:24:56.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不管你要去找谁\N{\rYUANWEN}whoever you were running to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.75,0:25:00.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你都能保证他们的安全 你会把他们带给我们吗\N{\rYUANWEN}you could keep them safe, you could bring them to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.59,0:25:06.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,家人 朋友 爱 不管是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}Family, friends, a lov- - I don't give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.76,0:25:08.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,无论我们什么时候找到他们\N{\rYUANWEN}They will be spared from our march,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.30,0:25:10.14,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们都不会被我们清除\N{\rYUANWEN}whenever we would have found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.43,0:25:14.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我愿意冒这个险\N{\rYUANWEN}I'lI take that chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.68,0:25:17.06,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我愿意为你冒这个险\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm taking that chance on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.91,0:25:30.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,波特兰会被摧毁\N{\rYUANWEN}Portland will die,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.53,0:25:33.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,而这支军队将接手公民共和国\N{\rYUANWEN}and this force will take over the Civic Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.74,0:25:35.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们会从郊区开始进军\N{\rYUANWEN}We will begin our march on the countryside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:38.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,下一个世界将会开始\N{\rYUANWEN}The Next World will begin,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.04,0:25:43.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,通过这个世界 我们将以某种方式生存下来\N{\rYUANWEN}and through that, somehow, some way, we will survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.25,0:25:46.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只有推倒一切才能重来\N{\rYUANWEN}We will burn things to bring things back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.38,0:25:50.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杀戮之剑即是赋予生命之剑\N{\rYUANWEN}The sword that kills is the sword that brings life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.27,0:26:05.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以剑起誓\N{\rYUANWEN}Swear on the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.98,0:26:08.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我问你个问题吧 格莱姆斯\N{\rYUANWEN}Let me ask you a question, Grimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.90,0:26:10.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会看着你的眼睛问你这个问题\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm just gonna ask it and look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.62,0:26:18.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,以剑起誓\N{\rYUANWEN}Swear on the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.25,0:26:20.04,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别让它得逞\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't let it take.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.19,0:26:47.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你为什么回来\N{\rYUANWEN}Why did you come back? l Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.53,0:26:48.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你走了 你死了\N{\rYUANWEN}You were gonel You were dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.11,0:26:50.74,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你本可以救下你想救之人\N{\rYUANWEN}You could've saved whoever you wanted to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.90,0:26:52.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后拯救整个世界 为什么\N{\rYUANWEN}and then saved the world. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.53,0:26:54.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,世界不会终结\N{\rYUANWEN}The world isn't gonna end!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.41,0:26:56.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,会的 我要确保我们不会毁灭\N{\rYUANWEN}It is! I'm trying to make sure we don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.88,0:27:07.13,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,该死的奥卡福\N{\rYUANWEN}Goddamn Okafor!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.17,0:27:10.92,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我从失去过儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}I never lost my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.05,0:27:12.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我迷失了自己\N{\rYUANWEN}I lost myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.93,0:27:16.68,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他把我救了回来 我老婆把我救了回来\N{\rYUANWEN}He brought me back. My wife brought me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.39,0:27:21.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们是杀戮之剑\N{\rYUANWEN}We re the sword that kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.06,0:27:24.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们是赋予生命之剑\N{\rYUANWEN}We're the sword that gives life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.15,0:27:27.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一次生命 不可阻挡的生命\N{\rYUANWEN}One life. One unstoppable life.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.23,0:27:28.52,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们没死\N{\rYUANWEN}We're not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.45,0:27:35.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,死的是你\N{\rYUANWEN}You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.76,0:28:00.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,索恩 我是格莱姆斯 完毕\N{\rYUANWEN}Thorne? It's Grimes, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.60,0:28:02.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,收到 完毕\N{\rYUANWEN}Thorne: Copy. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.02,0:28:06.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我收到简报了 我们晚点再谈\N{\rYUANWEN}I got the briefing. We'll talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.40,0:28:08.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比尔在全员出动前\N{\rYUANWEN}Beale went to the woods to be on his own
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.44,0:28:10.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,独自一人去了树林 完毕\N{\rYUANWEN}before the all- hands, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.73,0:28:12.53,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想现在碰头吗 完毕\N{\rYUANWEN}Do you want to meet now? Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.11,0:28:16.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比尔已经给我安排活儿了\N{\rYUANWEN}Beale gave me something to do already.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.45,0:28:17.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,完毕\N{\rYUANWEN}Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.54,0:29:50.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rYUANWEN}Damn it
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.37,0:29:52.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,必须去做\N{\rYUANWEN}Got to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.60,0:31:29.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,瑞克\N{\rYUANWEN}Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.97,0:31:32.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们不能回家 还不能\N{\rYUANWEN}We can't go home. Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.69,0:31:34.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-不  -你知道他们会做什么吗\N{\rYUANWEN}No. Do you know what they're gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.94,0:31:36.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我拿到了梯队报告 你怎么\N{\rYUANWEN}I got the Echelon. How did you-
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.61,0:31:38.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们有一整个帐篷的炸弹\N{\rYUANWEN}They have an entire tent of bombs out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.57,0:31:40.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们已经把孩了们疏散了\N{\rYUANWEN}They're evacuating the kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.44,0:31:42.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后就是一整个城市的人 瑞克\N{\rYUANWEN}then it's a whole city of people, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.95,0:31:44.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行动已经在进行中了\N{\rYUANWEN}This is happening now.
